<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>RFID Registration Successful - {{organizationName}}</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          'Inter',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1f2937;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        padding: 20px;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .header {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 32px 40px 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        position: relative;
      }

      .header::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #059669, #10b981, #34d399, #059669);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: successShift 3s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes successShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .logo::before {
        content: 'üì°';
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: #4b5563;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }

      .success-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5 0%, #d1fae5 100%);
        border: 1px solid #10b981;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .success-banner::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #059669, #10b981, #34d399, #059669);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: successShift 3s ease infinite;
      }

      .success-icon {
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: block;
        animation: bounce 2s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes bounce {
        0%,
        20%,
        50%,
        80%,
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        40% {
          transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        60% {
          transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
      }

      .success-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #065f46;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .success-description {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #059669;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .rfid-card {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
        border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        margin: 32px 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .rfid-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #059669, #10b981, #34d399, #059669);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: rfidShift 4s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes rfidShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .rfid-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .rfid-icon {
        font-size: 32px;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #10b981);
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .rfid-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #065f46;
      }

      .rfid-info {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .rfid-field {
        background: white;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .rfid-label {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .rfid-value {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
      }

      .rfid-id {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #059669;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
      }

      .status-active {
        color: #10b981;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .status-active::before {
        content: '‚óè';
        color: #10b981;
        animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%,
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
        50% {
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
      }

      .features-list {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .features-title {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .features-title::before {
        content: '‚ö°';
      }

      .features-list ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .features-list li {
        padding: 8px 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .features-list li::before {
        content: '‚úì';
        color: #10b981;
        font-weight: 600;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: #ecfdf5;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .security-notice {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #92400e;
      }

      .security-notice::before {
        content: 'üîê';
        margin-right: 8px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 32px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .footer-brand {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .footer-tagline {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .support-link {
        color: #059669;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .support-link:hover {
        color: #047857;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px;
        }

        .container {
          border-radius: 12px;
          max-width: 100%;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 24px 20px 20px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .rfid-info {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .rfid-header {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .rfid-card {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .success-banner {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }
      }

      @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .container {
          max-width: 900px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 48px 60px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 40px 60px 32px;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 40px 60px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='logo'>{{organizationName}}</div>
        <h1>RFID Registration Complete</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <div class='success-banner'>
          <div class='success-icon'>üéâ</div>
          <div class='success-title'>Registration Successful!</div>
          <div class='success-description'>Your RFID card has been activated and
            is ready to use</div>
        </div>

        <div class='greeting'>Hello {{firstName}},</div>

        <div class='description'>
          Excellent! Your RFID card has been successfully registered and linked
          to your
          {{organizationName}}
          account. You now have access to all our tech-enabled features and
          facilities.
        </div>

        <div class='rfid-card'>
          <div class='rfid-header'>
            <div class='rfid-icon'>üì°</div>
            <div class='rfid-title'>RFID Card Information</div>
          </div>

          <div class='rfid-info'>
            <div class='rfid-field'>
              <div class='rfid-label'>Card ID</div>
              <div class='rfid-value rfid-id'>{{rfidId}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class='rfid-field'>
              <div class='rfid-label'>Status</div>
              <div class='rfid-value status-active'>Active</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='features-list'>
          <div class='features-title'>What you can do with your RFID card:</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Access CSGUILD facilities and labs</li>
            <li>Quick login to your account</li>
            <li>Automated attendance tracking</li>
            <li>Participate in RFID-enabled events</li>
            <li>Access exclusive member areas</li>
            <li>Seamless integration with our tech ecosystem</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class='security-notice'>
          <strong>Security Reminder:</strong>
          Please keep your RFID card safe and secure. If you lose your card or
          suspect unauthorized use, report it immediately to our support team
          for deactivation and replacement.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='footer-brand'>The {{organizationName}} Team</div>
        <div class='footer-tagline'>Connecting you to the future of technology</div>
        <div>
          Questions about your RFID card? Contact us at
          <a
            href='mailto:{{supportEmail}}'
            class='support-link'
          >{{supportEmail}}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>